  "title": "fix(deps): update dependency documentation to ^5.0.0",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation\">documentation</a> from <code>v^4.0.0-rc.1</code> to <code>v^5.0.0</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>documentationjs/documentation</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"532\">5.3.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/c746c9b0ae980861cfbb5d436639a748b61f626a\"><code>c746c9b</code></a> chore(release): 5.3.2</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/de19175980cb1ab732f6c5772d289ed37540c837\"><code>de19175</code></a> test: Add tests for moduleFilters, tiny typo fix</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/2605a3b5fd607ed7db065cddaa409a1f599ab99d\"><code>2605a3b</code></a> test: Tests for dependency resolution</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/61b6976594cc16fdfb01d4fb3288836d397edc58\"><code>61b6976</code></a> test: More tests</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/8779369ce5922a3e90c56710048dd541f478d5ba\"><code>8779369</code></a> test: Add stronger jest tests for inference</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/adf1bd04c0de3957a9ed50040978fbe6d0356ee5\"><code>adf1bd0</code></a> test: Add specific test for quoted properties in type definitions</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/7fc6ca8f73113f9f1d9309b878a12c3bc9ac589b\"><code>7fc6ca8</code></a> fix: special property names in flowtypes</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/a8201748e6fec71febc914252381a1a8459ab6d9\"><code>a820174</code></a> chore: Update tests for latest release (#&#8203;912)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"531\">5.3.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/bc470756366af819d005196da804f423908b8231\"><code>bc47075</code></a> chore(release): 5.3.1</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/29601d91a0a952af3588df0ad1b30cadafe3c47f\"><code>29601d9</code></a> chore: Update yarn.lock</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/b97241f8d16bb7aec3ad5f777bc3166e8da7b94e\"><code>b97241f</code></a> fix: Enable dynamicImport plugin to support import() syntax (#&#8203;903)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/67c0a29e580067a83f17a4fac35eb135d420aea0\"><code>67c0a29</code></a> chore(package): update babel-jest to version 21.0.0 (#&#8203;900)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/125a577199f70b789701edf6d4581935d312cbf4\"><code>125a577</code></a> fix: regression in toc causing crash</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/5bdbf1f870b7add55d8ae5fa0e8cabe91d200458\"><code>5bdbf1f</code></a> fix: cover more hideconstructor cases</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/0307dbaaa668d9338ec5f1f3711f16895ac1fb49\"><code>0307dba</code></a> chore: Update test fixtures</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"530\">5.3.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/769ed235d1a1fb77f2a8fb97b798591e991ea730\"><code>769ed23</code></a> chore(release): 5.3.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/a04b6fd61dd9edf3b8d83d2b91857e2535c4e7e8\"><code>a04b6fd</code></a> fix: <a href=\"https://github.com/name\">@name</a> tag disconnects comment (#&#8203;897)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/c94412a7aa15e5c15f23861c9616916f831e2b49\"><code>c94412a</code></a> feat: groups in toc (#&#8203;895)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/7a07d5118d12a575e20b92615903ad0fa753f30e\"><code>7a07d51</code></a> feat: implement <a href=\"https://github.com/hideconstructor\">@hideconstructor</a> (#&#8203;898)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/2df7d3e54bbeef0da977d9440685e73e39759909\"><code>2df7d3e</code></a> style: Making return type params consistent with the rest of the code base (#&#8203;894)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/b486988cddf6d08add3a1923d988208e94bd7f62\"><code>b486988</code></a> chore: Update tests for new tag</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"522\">5.2.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/2df8b4c196cf321d10df5fbb0a14dec7e23bb6a5\"><code>2df8b4c</code></a> chore(release): 5.2.2</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/64a057369e31f6c62e1569cd592891d07b44820a\"><code>64a0573</code></a> chore: Update yarn.lock</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/1286a1ff8725825cfceca378907fcd81bb53ec35\"><code>1286a1f</code></a> fix($compile): prevent babel from transpiling non-module scripts in default_theme&#x27;s assets</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/1ba5f03ad200f92c1bb4b2f3c1d899c51452a1ea\"><code>1ba5f03</code></a> chore(package): update flow-bin to version 0.53.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/aab6f90bc733e9c52023568a65c92c35914f9e81\"><code>aab6f90</code></a> chore: Use tilde dependency on babel-generator</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/eddfcc29857b0349c01bc7b69e13f1958aafcceb\"><code>eddfcc2</code></a> chore: Update tests for new tag</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/762bca9d50730bdef6a70d0e647f4baaccb5bfa1\"><code>762bca9</code></a> chore(package): update regenerator-runtime to version 0.11.0</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"521\">5.2.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/e9d734b6a6eb1087bce0d1c261200e7b4b7ab26c\"><code>e9d734b</code></a> chore(release): 5.2.1</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/8278fa442c28688e790668b6c04f11f3c89db08e\"><code>8278fa4</code></a> chore: Update yarn.lock</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/25d0cfaadef3182a60efebf39d5ae3c9f5f866df\"><code>25d0cfa</code></a> build: Use stage-0 and es2015 for transpiling documentation.js</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/6a8a3f6310cfbf711dffab721ec67eb2703a90ce\"><code>6a8a3f6</code></a> ci: Reduce node version on CircleCI to 4</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/e0b605f8177c24426ae029bcd3edbe542060bf0a\"><code>e0b605f</code></a> style: Avoid optional parameter syntax</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/233edb834507b4452b72413254a7fcaa848c761e\"><code>233edb8</code></a> chore(package): update tmp to version 0.0.33 (#&#8203;877)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/ffdfa21788cb8c51e0063a3b2c7b97cb9b94fc01\"><code>ffdfa21</code></a> chore: Update tests for new tag</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"520\">5.2.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/77e348cfd0068b173c5381902a7167d49c2f030d\"><code>77e348c</code></a> chore(release): 5.2.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/0324865ad55beb95f97f9d53280e687fd7c7cab9\"><code>0324865</code></a> fix: make html and markdown second option optional (#&#8203;871)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/23aa981c30939b7cbe4ba07534b1c209b8fb6783\"><code>23aa981</code></a> feat: convert Flow&#x27;s ThisTypeAnnotation to a doctrine NameExpression (#&#8203;870)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/e73dd982a72cf110fd491df96059f7211aba5479\"><code>e73dd98</code></a> chore: Updated Flow.js dependency on 0.52.0 (#&#8203;862)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/aa3496af90508188a7652010dce501bba6917817\"><code>aa3496a</code></a> fix: alphabetical sort and add flow notation to sort file (#&#8203;861)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/4911ba6240775c7f936b0c96258906d947073b50\"><code>4911ba6</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;866 from anthony-redFox/fixTests</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/2dfe7427ae3095270d1a495d31476b1890123776\"><code>2dfe742</code></a> Fixed unit tests after put the tag v5.1.1</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"511\">5.1.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/0980113f40b3cb45186e9b8ef54c78a875c88290\"><code>0980113</code></a> chore(release): 5.1.1</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/ecf16bdaa0385bfc2d466d4ce9fd079bfd4791f1\"><code>ecf16bd</code></a> fix: cli options should override package.json options</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/dccb15160d1f0a244d1108b64bfa523a0a0b5467\"><code>dccb151</code></a> fix(theme): Remove dead stepsibling navigation code</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/2f200ecc79a580d656c22009bfce7f1631206b9b\"><code>2f200ec</code></a> chore: Update test snapshots for release</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"510\">5.1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/54332ecda92e5e953f1762ba073dce5f1ba3e91a\"><code>54332ec</code></a> chore(release): 5.1.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/6509ae813e2a9d5cde6fb4d7373451ad8ee82b71\"><code>6509ae8</code></a> feat(theme): Flexible sidebar for default theme</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/9433ec605eef8ec12213730f0d0bc448f43aa719\"><code>9433ec6</code></a> test: Remove unnecessary callbacks from tests</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/c3cdaeab6505e87c20c692cc08bcd2caf7664e31\"><code>c3cdaea</code></a> test: Run input tests</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/d1320f694e9a8bb491fd7498c3b96c5422ebbb09\"><code>d1320f6</code></a> chore: Update test snapshot for new version</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/81fa4b0327069f9993666f83479d7c58ee25c54b\"><code>81fa4b0</code></a> build: Run build on prepublish</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/dddac190094eb8908064f5516a5d2b8a05cc3751\"><code>dddac19</code></a> fix(scripts): Remove changelog package.json task</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"501\">5.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/2eb09131a008a72434859eed058624c1994260a5\"><code>2eb0913</code></a> chore(release): 5.0.1</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/edeb80c58239aa5c43ae46f6ea2996e4179160cd\"><code>edeb80c</code></a> chore: Update yarn.lock</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"500\">5.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/de4809247434842fc736bb7ff90d351e1d935e4f\"><code>de48092</code></a> chore(release): 5.0.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/documentationjs/documentation/commit/5b373ff2fe89f4170266870deb71e4afc517e331\"><code>5b373ff</code></a> revert(polyglot): Remove polyglot mode</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
